metadata.name: Johaneett
metadata.description:
A rising cybermodel posing for a renowned Web3 fashion magazine. 

"Johaneett is a blue chip, and every investor adores her," said the editor-in-chief of the world-renowned fashion and lifestyle publisher Vogu3.

1 of 1 edition
Digital sculpt + motion graphics + SFX 
1512 x 2000 pixels
